title: The Who - LIVE 08/04/2002 Encore Series [320k MP3] NYC
description:
2-CD set of the complete and unedited concert recorded from the soundboard and mixed by The Who engineering team. These professionally mastered and manufactured CDs (NOT CD-Rs). Each CD set comes in a cardboard sleeve package with exclusive artwork, designed especially for the Encore Series and authorized by the band.
